---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Midwives — Testimonials That Build Trust With Expecting Parents | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display authentic birth testimonials for your midwifery practice. Let positive birth stories attract expecting parents choosing their care provider. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Midwives</p>
        <h1>The birth story your clients tell is your most powerful marketing</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Expecting parents research their care provider more carefully than almost any other decision they'll make. SocialProof captures your clients' birth stories and displays them where researching parents can find you — and feel safe choosing you.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why midwifery practices struggle to capture their reputation</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Birth stories are shared in mom groups, not on Google</h3>
            <p>Your clients rave about you in Facebook groups and to their pregnant friends. That word-of-mouth is real — but it doesn't show up when someone Googles "midwife near me."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 The new baby fog is real</h3>
            <p>Postpartum clients have a newborn. Asking for a Google review in those first weeks is asking a lot. A simple link they can fill in 2 minutes changes everything.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 High-stakes choices need deep trust</h3>
            <p>Choosing a midwife is one of the most personal decisions a family makes. Strangers on Yelp don't build that trust. A story from someone who was exactly where they are does.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>6–8 weeks postpartum, when clients have settled into their new normal, send a collect link. "Would you share a bit about your experience?" Most will — and they'll mean every word.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions in your dashboard. Select the testimonials that capture what makes your care special — the presence, the patience, the support through hard moments.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag on your About page or services page. Works with any website builder — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Midwifery Practices</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + full testimonials</h3>
            <p>Capture the narrative — not just 5 stars but the story of what it felt like to be supported through pregnancy and birth.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Family photos (optional)</h3>
            <p>Some clients love to share a birth announcement photo. Others prefer privacy. You approve everything — complete control.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Warm, professional design</h3>
            <p>Customize colors and layout to match your practice. Reassuring and evidence-based, just like your care philosophy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 Simple mobile form</h3>
            <p>Clients fill it in minutes on their phone during a quiet moment. No account creation, no review platform login required.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 Sensitive data, protected</h3>
            <p>You approve every testimonial before it's public. Clients share only what they're comfortable with. Their stories, their terms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
